commands.name: az consumption reservation summary list
commands.summary: List reservation summaries for daily or monthly by order Id or reservation id.
commands.syntax:
az consumption reservation summary list --grain {daily, monthly}
                                        --reservation-order-id
                                        [--end-date]
                                        [--max-items]
                                        [--next-token]
                                        [--reservation-id]
                                        [--start-date]
